{#-
  Auth-EmailVerification — terminal "check your email" pattern (Ring 3).

  Composes `_auth-shell` (title null — inner Empty owns the h1) + Empty
  (lg, h1, icon=check — see §1 Doctrine for icon-choice rationale) +
  Button × 1-2 (primary Resend + optional secondary Back-to-login).

  Pure server-rendered terminal page. 0 Stimulus controller.
  Typical entry point : post-Register flow (user signs up → consumer's
  auth back-end sends a verification email → redirects user here).

  Microcopy : body "Email envoyé. Vérifie ta boîte (et tes spams)."

  Icon choice : `check` (action-complete) instead of envelope/mail. The
  Lucide curated 30-set does NOT include `mail.svg`. Pre-existing bug :
  Auth-Register + Auth-ForgotPassword success states reference `icon: 'mail'`
  which would throw at render time. This pattern uses the curated `check`
  substitut to ship a working integration. A future update should either add
  mail.svg to curated set OR rewrite those templates.

  See `docs/specs/ring3/Auth-EmailVerification.md` for the full spec.
-#}

{%- set title             = title             | default('theme.auth.email-verification.title'|trans) -%}
{%- set body              = body              | default('theme.auth.email-verification.body'|trans) -%}
{%- set resendLabel       = resendLabel       | default('theme.auth.email-verification.resend-cta'|trans) -%}
{%- set resendHref        = resendHref        | default('#') -%}
{%- set backToLoginLabel  = backToLoginLabel  | default('theme.auth.email-verification.back-to-login-cta'|trans) -%}
{%- set backToLoginHref   = backToLoginHref   | default(null) -%}
{%- set htmlId            = htmlId            | default('cremona-auth-email-verification') -%}
{%- set className         = className         | default('') -%}

{% embed '@cremona/components/_auth-shell/_auth-shell.html.twig' with {
  title: null,
  htmlId: htmlId,
  variant: 'default',
  className: ('cremona-auth-email-verification ' ~ className)|trim,
} %}
  {% block content %}
    {% embed '@cremona/components/empty/empty.html.twig' with {
      title: title,
      body: body,
      icon: 'check',
      size: 'lg',
      titleLevel: 'h1',
      htmlId: htmlId ~ '-empty',
    } %}
      {% block actions %}
        {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
          label: resendLabel,
          variant: 'secondary',
          size: 'md',
          href: resendHref,
        } %}
        {% if backToLoginHref %}
          {% include '@cremona/components/button/button.html.twig' with {
            label: backToLoginLabel,
            variant: 'ghost',
            size: 'md',
            href: backToLoginHref,
            iconLeading: 'arrow-left',
          } %}
        {% endif %}
      {% endblock %}
    {% endembed %}
  {% endblock %}
{% endembed %}
